  componentName: REF1
  specifications: (E+H FMR51-134B/0)
  description: 'These radar level transmitters monitor the water level between Tank
    1 and Tank 2, corresponding to the setpoint on the control panel (Level Controller).
    Each sensor has a maximum

    measurement range of 25 meters and is capable
    of detecting the water level down to the tank bottom. The total water volume
    (QT) across both tanks can be calculated as:

    

    QT=Tank 1 level (REF1)+Tank
    2 level (REF2)'
